item.title: Ted Cruz biograph
item.description: Senator Ted Cruz Biograph Rafael Edward Cruz is an American attorney and politician. He is currently serving as the Junior U.S. Senator for Texas. He was born in Alberta, Canada on December 22nd, 1970. He went to two private high schools, Faith West Academy and Second Baptist High School. He graduated from there in 1988 as a valedictorian. He went to Princeton University in 1992. He graduated cum Laude with a B.
